msgid "[Nextcloud Talk](https://f-droid.org/packages/com.nextcloud.talk2/) had a major update to 2.0.0 and now has chat! (Including paginated scrolling, mentions auto-completion and other nice tricks.) Other major features include client certificate based authentication, voice-only calls, significantly improved calls UI, and endless loading for contacts & remote search. Note that this app requires you to have your own server."
