#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: _posts/2018-12-13-twif-34-f-droid-is-a-planet.md
msgid "Since we've mentioned SimpleEmail, its upstream app **[FairEmail](https://f-droid.org/packages/eu.faircode.email/)** got plenty of updates and fixes in the mean time, way too many to list here. What we can mention is that the app has lowered its device requirements so now it's compatible with Android 5 too."
